> 1) PCMCIA
>         Repeatable:
>         Insert pcmcia-to-scsi card (aha152x_cs.o loads)
>         mount /mnt/zip && ls /mnt/zip && umount /mnt/zip
>         pull pcmcia-to-scsi card --> COMPLETE FREEZE
You cannot hot eject SCSI adapters even if there are no mounted
filesystems.  You must use "cardctl eject" first.
